{"tid":997093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南亞惡童蝦蝦霸霸】偷竊掟石霸地盤撩交打 土瓜灣街坊：唔敢行近佢哋","createTime":"2019-01-26T23:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T13:30:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"fbdb47f8ab5a4ca4a7b8e9854fff5820eb7eb6fa","tid":997093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:26:08.000Z","msg":"近年來，涉及南亞人的罪案，愈來愈多。他們的勢力範圍，亦由元朗郊區，蔓延到市區。其中土瓜灣一帶，更出現大批聯群結隊的南亞童黨，不時會惹事欺凌。 <br />\n白太（化名）住在土瓜灣，育有三子。早前她如常帶三子到土瓜灣遊樂場嬉戲，期間短暫離開處理公事，未幾接到11歲長子倫仔（化名）來電，指在足球場被南亞童踢傷眼睛。<br />\n倫仔向記者指出，當天與同學受兩名一高一矮南亞童邀請踢足球，期間南亞童竟以足球襲擊他的同學，更從背後以手勒頸。眼見同學被欺負，他出手推開南亞童，但遭其南亞朋友挑釁打架，隨後他們更召來大批童黨推撞兩人。<br />\n倫仔後來離開現場，及後踢足球期間，疑被南亞童刻意用足球踢傷眼睛。<br />\n白太表示，小朋友嬉戲期間受傷屬平常之事，本來對少數族裔人士亦無不滿。但不明白南亞童為何要求兒子打架解決事情。其後，她將事件放至社交網站提醒其他家長提防，引來大批土瓜灣家長回應。<br />\n於社交網站帖文中發現，不少土瓜灣家長亦有類似遭遇，眾人矛頭直指區內南亞童黨，曾眾目睽睽之下意圖搶去港童的滑板車，更會霸佔遊樂場不予港童使用，更有成年人被南亞童黨擲石頭攻擊等。<br />\n本刊記者到訪土瓜灣遊樂場向南亞小朋友查詢，期間向南亞童展示有關擲石頭童黨的照片，該受訪南亞童稱認識照片中人士，更向記者說：「佢哋有打人！」<br />\n九龍城區區議員林博表示，確實收到不少土瓜灣居民的投訴，指南亞童經常踢足球時有意無意地射中途人，更有土瓜灣遊樂場公廁被南亞童以濕廁紙團擲向天花板、夜歸女士被南亞人士尾隨、醉酒南亞人深夜打破玻璃瓶及大聲叫囂等事件發生，對土瓜灣居民生活造成滋擾。<br />\n但林博認為，南亞人亦有好壞之分，部分較為頑皮的童黨可能因為失業或沒有上學，故此較多時間在街上流連，但另一方面生活較為穩定，有正常工作及需要上學的南亞人，亦能與本地居民相處融洽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_651545_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_651545_0&d=Apzw%2BpnRtpznMpZPiMpR2Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=57e6ce09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_651545_0&h=29e7134e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_651545_0</a>"},{"pid":"3edc93b030104541675d63e1820e7f9aab2a8bfb","tid":997093,"uid":202278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:29:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d9417fbdbc485eac4157cc6377d80ef2b729b08","tid":997093,"uid":70227,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:33:15.000Z","msg":"起集中營捉晒佢地入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南亞毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c886a1e4dbae364102537e3e72d6b937aa0936","tid":997093,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:40:34.000Z","msg":"張超雄:南亞人都有好人"},{"pid":"7c18b5f6e6e91a94cafe6a59cd55040af3aafb1b","tid":997093,"uid":34410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:48:07.000Z","msg":"邊個左膠同情d啡皮狗應該自己收容哂佢地去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb76084f726f66ae21ee15596b06600ac9e47b","tid":997093,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:05:38.000Z","msg":"報紙佬又作新聞破壞港南關係?"},{"pid":"991e11a2a5282dd8c6ae1f276506321cc65ef60b","tid":997093,"uid":152701,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"2019年<br />\n仲覺得南亞人無咩問題<br />\n你個仔唔盲都算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算我而家住太古好少見南亞垃圾<br />\n我都同我個仔講 一見南亞人唔好理立即走<br />\n生番來無得同佢地講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac011ef4cbfe481997f8be608ab7b09835d0756","tid":997093,"uid":60831,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:24:28.000Z","msg":"之前話做衰野嘅係假難民<br />\n話土生土長係好人班食屎狗呢?"},{"pid":"6ec35c71a8df7e839efdaad57d2cb630340119b3","tid":997093,"uid":136735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"多撚謝 超雄哥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb195ca3084a0fa32a06db84db96551474a1403b","tid":997093,"uid":242,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>又係南亞狗</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6203319f63050a55302fc90c1ae01bcf4b2fed56","tid":997093,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3P3ve6jhRqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3P3ve6jhRqY&d=Apzw%2BpnRtpznMpZPiMpR2Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c15cbefd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3P3ve6jhRqY</a>"},{"pid":"87fc93e6288ba7d4a893af1f1e618b574e838a6a","tid":997093,"uid":35014,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7ca08bcbaf6ce036ebb257a6cb10a30a3ff3706","tid":997093,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:45:11.000Z","msg":"要李小龍上身一個打十個先得"},{"pid":"9f9f49b639cd3a76c0bdcce3281eab36a7f3fb0f","tid":997093,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"咁似啲未開發既土著"},{"pid":"456e3df70a01a8a424a89aac6528874aeb3567ec","tid":997093,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"點解李小龍嘅精神冇晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好做東亞病夫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e41770629702fdef91e5bf331c9ca4cdeced4","tid":997093,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"小蝻蟲係欺善怕惡<br />\n我不知幾想比佢哋挑機跟住打柒一兩隻再走<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋避開成年男人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c8e1fd5eab307dd66fae1cfef98f5a243a8ee9","tid":997093,"uid":206925,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"張超雄又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3046097b9331443f26c2be4e7820bff82eac4d","tid":997093,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"張超雄"},{"pid":"f57b722bd77ece12a8ce250de3d5c8c791b11a7d","tid":997093,"uid":4674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3e41770629702fdef91e5bf331c9ca4cdeced4","tid":997093,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"小蝻蟲係欺善怕惡<br />\n我不知幾想比佢哋挑機跟住打柒一兩隻再走<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋避開成年男人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"咁組團一齊落去"},{"pid":"ddc518aced2247216662c627a0b3c6ebd48507ab","tid":997093,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:12:27.000Z","msg":"張超雄正仆街"},{"pid":"75436858f1a96b863f78e6d108f66244ff69e436","tid":997093,"uid":182244,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"好簡單，你一個民族畀人印象差，見到你個民族既人自然憎恨。<br />\n<br />\n你見到澳洲人，話澳洲人好nice，唔通你又話我歧視澳洲人？因為澳州都有壞人？<br />\n<br />\n我夠知南亞人好人，但講到一個總族畀人既感覺，當然係大睇啦。<br />\n<br />\n問心個句，如果你有小朋友住個區，如果十宗傷人案有七宗係南亞人做，其餘三宗係本地人，我好相信家長會叫見到南亞就行開，理鬼佢有冇好人。<br />\n<br />\n係呀，我地香港人好多人唔鍾意南亞，佢地有無檢討過？凡事必有因，又唔見我地憎美國人，佢地喺香港咪又係少數。<br />\n<br />\n大家問心個句，唔好自己呃自己"},{"pid":"c0337af80a838476511964ff34086484744fe554","tid":997093,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d9417fbdbc485eac4157cc6377d80ef2b729b08","tid":997093,"uid":70227,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T23:33:15.000Z","msg":"起集中營捉晒佢地入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南亞毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66a80fb64276d3576382b51276c6c4c2d3fec74","tid":997093,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3e41770629702fdef91e5bf331c9ca4cdeced4","tid":997093,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"小蝻蟲係欺善怕惡<br />\n我不知幾想比佢哋挑機跟住打柒一兩隻再走<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋避開成年男人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"咁夠薑同大人打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b3f240427b3512837ac9c05b971791dc4b339c","tid":997093,"uid":189328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"成日講有好人有壞人， 佢地班壞人呀長期犯法都冇畀人拉， 我點會對呢班人有好感， 如果 政府肯做野 用d方法減少佢斑壞人， 我都會尊重佢全部種族， 有時見到佢地有班人係想融入社會 努力讀書工作， 就係政府冇做野 令到香港人對佢地反感 融入唔到社會， 而家佢地係街度聯群結隊我只會聯想到犯罪， 對一個種族既睇法係佢地既行為產生， 如果佢地壞人得到適當嘅處理加上 好個班既努力 我相信香港人冇人會對 佢地反感"},{"pid":"4e8cec7b5dbccaef5bcccf0cf3101ecdcb7a01d5","tid":997093,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"南亞（物攻）vs香港（魔攻）<br />\n<br />\n史上兩大邪惡民族對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}